@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xgrpau(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    v0 = (wp.cos(v1) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.10) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.11)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.69) / 0.86) + ((v2 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.11) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.11)))
    data[tid] = v0
